oices to Helios & Matheson for services he claimed were rendered by Kaleido=
scope and a different company he owned, prosecutors said. Helios & Matheson=
 paid the invoices, even though neither it nor MoviePass were involved in t=
he Coachella event, prosecutors said.=C2=A0

