oryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000;=
 text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-=
color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  were=
 indicted</a>, accused of securities fraud. This was not a well-run company=
, nor one that was committed to the highest ethical standards, nor one that=
 was all that careful with money. If you worked there and wanted to submit =
$260,000 of fake invoices to pay for a party at Coachella, would anyone sto=
p you? No, it turns out, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/30640231.258438/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVz=
LzIwMjMtMDItMjIvbW92aWVwYXNzLWV4ZWMtYWxsZWdlZGx5LWVtYmV6emxlZC10by1wYXktZm9=
yLWNvYWNoZWxsYS1wYXJ0eT9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMjIzMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPW=
VtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzAyMjMmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduP=
W1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBdfe17b4d" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
